{"tid":1815771,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"杜絕捉鬼 全民black bloc","createTime":"2020-01-07T18:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T05:07:58.000Z","uid":326479,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac8b53713fbab7487007d62e30d5eeacb4e894b","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:38:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">既然和勇不分， 點解唔全民black bloc !<br />\n<br />\n既然和勇不分， 咁唔好淨係得把口講， 用你嘅衣著發聲！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">目的：</span><br />\n杜絕捉鬼等行為<br />\n保護勇武<br />\n提高搜證難度<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Imagine</span>： <br />\n如果之前1月1 有103萬個black bloc , 睇你點撚樣捉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">重點 for 和理非：</span><br />\n蒙面係合法㗎！<br />\n著黑衫黑褲黑鞋行街食飯都係合法㗎！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">乜野係blackbloc (bb), 簡單到c9 阿公阿婆係人都得:</span><br />\n黑褲+黑色有帽風褸/ 黑色有帽外套 , 到時先戴帽<br />\n加個黑色口罩已經足夠<br />\n袋： 黑色/深色背襄<br />\n鞋： 黑色嘅鞋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">和理非風險：</span><br />\n根本冇分別， 黑警濫捕， 銅鑼灣300 人著咩色衫都係會照拉 , 咁點解唔全部blackbloc 去行街. 唔好再天真地以為你著白色衫就冇事啦， 拉左7千幾人喇， 大把人唔係著黑衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">留意返:</span><br />\n- Blackbloc 唔等如勇武！<br />\n唔能夠用眼見嘅blackbloc 人數決定勇武人數<br />\n- 一定有分化撚話真係有鬼咁點？ 平時就係因為blackbloc 係少數, 黑警好容易認到邊d 係勇武/前線， 如果全條街都一樣，全部都係blackbloc 就冇噤容易， 目標係將非blackbloc變成少數！<br />\n- 其實6月開始一直都有人講全民blackbloc但冇人做，搞到好多無謂犧牲， 所以要正式再講多次<br />\n<br />\n請喺文宣加一句dress code: <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民black bloc </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果呢個建議有啲咩漏洞， 歡迎互吊出更好嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人 團結！<br />\n<br />\n和勇不分 全民blackbloc<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割席 不分化 不篤灰<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjUOPAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhjUOPAm.jpg&h=04ed7dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource 謝曬皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wfFFHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wfFFHq.jpg&h=2a08f2d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83d4da8160fb45066778c055f7b6aec8a8363c64","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 1"},{"pid":"49b69607512ced89f9571af4df86162c022b3517","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:41:54.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 2"},{"pid":"d471b6ec836fdf56fd4f41a1006c95d088249c7d","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:42:14.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 3"},{"pid":"5be63cc9cef2a0ce2f5ec30b1369ff84391833ae","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:42:30.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 4"},{"pid":"b9c53ae10aa34950e7f79255a27eefe946d26093","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:42:51.000Z","msg":"求幫推"},{"pid":"957d9611c584daa0017a98e1b5f397c8af61f5b2","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:43:08.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 5"},{"pid":"8e1d1bbc539edb8286cc41b8fd7d00434930167c","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:43:19.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 6"},{"pid":"90e1fc227d9388a4292e1dc1536379fc412ce51c","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 7"},{"pid":"dda44ada736bf6d576ecad72316b8c340de8324b","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 8"},{"pid":"2b105a8baafff46e3aa4b9feb905f047edfb3baf","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:44:15.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁 9"},{"pid":"da267b61ee3c086082782368e044e0be6463ec43","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,