itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"多謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> p 牌堅難推"},{"pid":"e9f9f0e26722d6e06dfc2642c3d8943946a728fb","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"657da36dcf19b9301bd2f72043e64d1e6af0e1ef","tid":1815771,"uid":259674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"冇錢買, 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"一定要出聲， 噤多tg 群，一定有家長/二手/ 舊衫可以支持你！仲有 , 我見到wolipay 有黃嘅社區二手店可買平貨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpKCOHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpKCOHg.png&h=682da5f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4344b8271c69120d899d77f2b76c597e975372d","tid":1815771,"uid":104171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:26:38.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n以前叫人攝衫就係驚有鬼<br />\n唔明點解而家好似覺得唔洗防咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捉鬼係應該嘅<br />\n只係應該要學識點樣捉<br />\n<br />\n勇武走唔切比鬼拉都發生過好多次啦<br />\n而家先走黎吹風話「唔好捉鬼」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a4ec6e1ee1abedb1ba5df76be9c69927aa8d8e","tid":1815771,"uid":262575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4344b8271c69120d899d77f2b76c597e975372d","tid":1815771,"uid":104171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:26:38.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n以前叫人攝衫就係驚有鬼<br />\n唔明點解而家好似覺得唔洗防咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捉鬼係應該嘅<br />\n只係應該要學識點樣捉<br />\n<br />\n勇武走唔切比鬼拉都發生過好多次啦<br />\n而家先走黎吹風話「唔好捉鬼」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:41:59.000Z","msg":"近期連登奇怪左好多，黑講到白，<br />\n唔捉鬼唔等於冇鬼，<br />\n尐鬼害左幾多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫捉鬼仲要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家吹唔着黑衫都要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街坊裝都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自由表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a789e487dbb417a01ab30d7bd3b9f6f650391d5a","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4344b8271c69120d899d77f2b76c597e975372d","tid":1815771,"uid":104171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:26:38.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n以前叫人攝衫就係驚有鬼<br />\n唔明點解而家好似覺得唔洗防咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捉鬼係應該嘅<br />\n只係應該要學識點樣捉<br />\n<br />\n勇武走唔切比鬼拉都發生過好多次啦<br />\n而家先走黎吹風話「唔好捉鬼」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"好， 假設行街期間有廿隻鬼混入左<br />\n你估佢地唔識攝衫咩？ 以前佢地淨係target住d blackbloc 就可以好容易埋勇武身， 然後幾隻㩒低一個勇武<br />\n<br />\n如果成條街全部都係blackbloc, 佢地target 邊個？ 即使俾佢睇住有人做野， 一返入人群就難跟。人數係我地著數嘅地方 , 可以加以利用<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講，和理非唔捉鬼加全民blackbloc 比捉鬼有多啲好處<br />\n<br />\n同埋，真係要捉鬼都留返俾勇武啦"},{"pid":"81874f467d2ff066a0745f56aaac7aca587a0480","tid":1815771,"uid":326479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8a4ec6e1ee1abedb1ba5df76be9c69927aa8d8e","tid":1815771,"uid":262575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4344b8271c69120d899d77f2b76c597e975372d","tid":1815771,"uid":104171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:26:38.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n以前叫人攝衫就係驚有鬼<br />\n唔明點解而家好似覺得唔洗防咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捉鬼係應該嘅<br />\n只係應該要學識點樣捉<br />\n<br />\n勇武走唔切比鬼拉都發生過好多次啦<br />\n而家先走黎吹風話「唔好捉鬼」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:41:59.000Z","msg":"近期連登奇怪左好多，黑講到白，<br />\n唔捉鬼唔等於冇鬼，<br />\n尐鬼害左幾多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫捉鬼仲要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家吹唔着黑衫都要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街坊裝都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自由表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"其實講乜都會有人屌， 只要互屌完可以幫到個運動就ok<br />\n<br />\n街坊裝3 個月前都仲可能有用， 和理非心理上會覺得安全d<br />\n但去到1月1 已經唔同晒， 著乜都鳩拉<br />\n當然，你仍然有自由著街坊裝<br />\n全民blackbloc 只係想為堅持和勇不分出一分力"},{"pid":"a4fb183e1e612c9d59150b69f4e5e9ade0466ceb","tid":1815771,"uid":112589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"［不捉鬼＝不分化？］鬼，或成瓦解運動的關鍵。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eKjoyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eKjoyS</a>"}]}